Methods-sum of digits

Write a program to find the sum of digits in a given number. Program to find the sum of digits of the given number is discussed here. 
For example, let the input number be 719. The sum of digits of 719 = 7 + 1 + 9 = 17
Input & Output Format:

Input consists of one integer.

Output consists of sum of digits.

program:
import java.util.Scanner;//scanner class
public class Sum//main class
{
    public static void main(String[] args)//function class
    {
      Scanner sc=new Scanner(System.in);//object class the code starts from here
      int a=sc.nextInt();//value1
      int b=0,t;
      while(a>0)
      {
          t=a%10;
          b+=t;
          a=a/10;
      }
      System.out.println(b);
    }
}
//class sum
class Sum1
{
    public static int sum(int a)//definition
    {
        int sum=a;
        return sum;
    }
}
